OLD utopia.2014.desc:0 "The [sentry_system.GetName] system at some point in galactic history evidently supported a vast orbital infrastructure of unusual proportions that has since been systematically demolished. There are large concentrations of debris in geostationary orbits around most planetary bodies in the system, including several massive space station hulks.\n\nThe largest of these hulks is a colossal §HSentry Array§!. Our initial scans suggest that when it was operational, this array was powerful enough to provide real-time sensor coverage over the entire galaxy."
NEW utopia.2014.desc:1 "At some point in galactic history, the [sentry_system.GetName] system evidently supported a vast orbital infrastructure of unusual proportions which has since been systematically demolished. There are large concentrations of debris in geostationary orbits around most of the planetary bodies in this system, including several massive space station hulks.\n\nThe largest of these is a colossal §HSentry Array§!. Our initial scans suggest that when it was operational, this array was powerful enough to provide real-time sensor coverage over the entire galaxy."
CN utopia.2014.desc:1 "证据表明，[sentry_system.GetName]星系在银河历史上的某个时刻支持过一个无比庞大的轨道设施，但它已经被系统地拆解了。大部分行星天体的的同步轨道上都密布着碎片，其中包括几个巨型空间站的笨重船体。\n\n其中最大的船体是一个巨大的§H监探阵列§!。我们的初步扫描显示，当它运行时，强大的阵列可以提供整个银河系的实时传感器覆盖。"
CN2 utopia.2014.desc:1 "在过去的某时，星系曾建有过一个体积异常巨大的轨道设施，后来被有组织地拆毁。此星系大部分天体的行星同步轨道上都弥漫着大量的残骸，当中不乏大型空间站的外壳。\n\n残骸中以一个庞大的§H哨兵阵列§!为最。经过我们初步的扫描结果推测，这个阵列强大到足以实时监控整个星系。"
CHANGE utopia.2014.desc:1 "证据表明，在银河历史上的某个时刻，[sentry_system.GetName]星系曾建有一个无比庞大的轨道设施，但它已经被系统地拆解了。星系内大部分行星天体的的同步轨道上都密布着碎片，其中包括几个巨型空间站的笨重船体。\n\n最大的船体是一个巨大的§H监探阵列§!。我们的初步扫描显示，在它运行时，强大的阵列可以提供整个银河系的实时传感器覆盖。"